	 _ran_caos_int($p,$m,$n,$$obj);
	 return $p;
       }
       ',
       Doc => <<'EOF',
=for ref

Returns values from Verhuls map with C<$r=4.0> and randomly chosen
C<$x0>. The values are scaled by C<$m>.

Usage:

=for usage

   $rng->ran_caos($m,$n);
EOF
);

